results.name: a(n) = floor(n/(product of nonzero digits of n)).
link: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
program: (PARI) ProdNzD(x)= { local(d, p=1); while (x>9, d=x%10; if (d, p*=d); x\=10); return(p*x) } { for (n=1, 1000, a=floor(n/ProdNzD(n)); write("b066577.txt", n, " ", a) ) } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, Mar 07 2010
